HEADWORD: Hypercritic
<hw>Hy`per*crit"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>hyper-</ets> + <ets>critic</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>hypercritique</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who is critical beyond measure
or reason; a carping critic; a captious censor.</def>
